data.text:
Follows the lives of eight very different couples in dealing with their love lives in various loosely interrelated tales all set during a frantic month before Christmas in London, England. Starring Emma Thompson, Alan Rickman, Hugh Grant, Colin Firth, and Liam Neeson.

Sponsored by Meaghan and Ryan Vogel

TICKETS

Tickets will be sold at the box office 30 minutes prior to screening.

Tickets are $5 for everyone. Additional cash donations will be accepted at the door to benefit the Wrightstown Food Cupboard.
